::DarkMouse::
She turned and walked down the hallway.  She felt like crying. Why did she 
feel like this.  She talked to herself.
"Well, after just walking off like that, he's bound to think I'm some sort 
of jerk or something.  Nice going DarkMouse.  Just blow your chance to get 
things straightened out."  She started to feel the tears well up in her 
optics and she ran to her room and slammed the door shut with a loud BANG!
